; Coverage test for format.cc line 265
; Test %$ field reference without a template (%/ separator).
; Using %$ outside of a secondary format (after %/) triggers an error
; because there is no prior template to reference.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%$1\n' -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Prior field reference, but no template
end test
